                    Anchor Elements & HyperTexts

Anchor Element ( a )
    |- navigate from one location to another location
    |- <a attributes > </a>
    |- attributes
        |- href  --> it holds the source file ( imp )
        |- target --> it shows destination
            |-     _self (default)
            |-     _blank (new page)
            |-     _parent 
            |-     _top 

            |-     'frameName'  

        |-  id   --> unique (#)

        colors 
        |- blue ( initial color) --- link="colorName"
        |- red  ( active color)  --- alink="colorName"
        |- violate (visited color) - vlink="colorName"            


        |- download -- it is used to download any link
